==English==

===Alternative Spellings===
*[[toucher]]

===Etymology===
From the Standard English to ''[[touch]]'' i.e. ''touching someone for money''

===Noun===
'''toucha'''
#(''[[Geordie]]'') a person who wants someting for nothing.
#:''"Yer a [[toucha]], yee just somthin for nothin aall the time!"''

